S3 generic for to_relational_data function.

to_relational_data.Rd

This function takes an object and converts into a TealData object, the primary data object for use in teal applications.

Usage

to_relational_data(data)

Arguments

data

TealDataset, TealDatasetConnector, data.frame, MultiAssayExperiment, list or function returning a named list.

Value

TealData object

Details

Passing a TealData into this function leaves the object unchanged.

Examples


to_relational_data(head(iris))
#> A TealData object containing 1 TealDataset/TealDatasetConnector object(s) as element(s):
#> --> Element 1:
#> A TealDataset object containing the following data.frame (6 rows and 5 columns):

#> 5          5.0         3.6          1.4         0.2  setosa
#> 6          5.4         3.9          1.7         0.4  setosa
